# LMS Home Page Requirements

## Core Architecture
- The LMS Home Page must be part of a **Single Page Application (SPA)** architecture with no full browser refreshes between sections.

## Dashboard Content
- Render a dashboard shell with sidebar navigation aligned to PRD routes (Dashboard, Courses, Registration, FAQ, External Data, Subscription, Sign In).
- Include a **Featured Course** widget, **Popular Courses** placeholders (C1, C2, C3), and an **FAQ** section on the home view.
- Preserve scroll-aware sidebar highlighting and accessible in-page navigation anchors.
